subject: Triathlon
New York City Triathlon
Deaths (Fatalities)
Swimming
lead_paragraph: A 40-year-old woman who was pulled from the swim leg of Sunday’s New York City Triathlon died at a hospital on Monday. A day earlier, a 64-year-old New Jersey man also died.
